name: Evans Morris
description: I am a very happy person, I like to have fun, walking, travel, play and smile. I am happy when I see a person around me comfortable. My hobbies are horseback riding, baseball, golf, music, reading, playing with animals, etc. I hate dishonesty and ruthless because life is full of errors and corrections. I love to laugh very often because it is one thing that keeps me going in life.
